資料庫更換步驟
mysql -u root -p

pip install mysqlclient

python 

create database mylcc default character set utf8 collate utf8_general_ci;

mysql -u root -p mylcc < mylcc.sql


============
1. pip3 install virtualenvwrapper-win

2. mkvirtualenv mydjango

deactivate 退出虛擬環境
workon 列出虛擬環境

3. workon mydjango
3-1. pip  install django
4. cd\
5. mkdir lccdjango
6. cd lccdjango 到檔案路徑
7. django-admin startproject  lcc
#建過不用再建立(cd\ 到lcc

python manage.py runserver
#執行 伺服器

資料庫有更動
需要執行
python manage.py midXXXX
python manage.py migrate


